@Roflcopterkklol

it was built in the VAB ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif) but now you can switch between radial and mirror mode at will ![:P](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif) (which is quite useful ^^)

@flixxbeatz, the long SRB is emptied and thrust set to 0 ![:P](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif)

it's used as an articulation point for the elevator platform retractation ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)

those long SRB's are useful, because they are among the longest parts in the game ![:P](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif), plus 1.25m wide and rounded - so it makes a nice structural part ![:P](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif)

